Investor Relations





















Investor Relations
Village Bank and Trust Financial Corp™ is organized under the laws of the Commonwealth of Virginia to engage in commercial and consumer banking. 

The Company’s wholly owned subsidiary, Village Bank®, is a traditional community bank offering deposit and loan services to individuals and businesses in the suburbs surrounding Richmond, Virginia.

Click here to access the Investor Relations site.







